started.

## Usage

### Installation

Install latest from the GitHub
[repository](https://github.com/Gaurav-Adlakha/test_5_dec):

``` sh
$ pip install git+https://github.com/Gaurav-Adlakha/test_5_dec.git
```

or from [conda](https://anaconda.org/Gaurav-Adlakha/test_5_dec)

``` sh
$ conda install -c Gaurav-Adlakha test_5_dec
```

or from [pypi](https://pypi.org/project/test_5_dec/)

``` sh
$ pip install test_5_dec
```
